            <div class="col-sm-6 col-m-6">
              <p id="mainPara" class="text-left">
                Metal Gear is a series of action-adventure stealth video games, created by Hideo Kojima (adjacent) and developed and published by Konami. The first game, Metal Gear, was released in 1987 for the MSX2. The player takes control of a special forces operative
                Solid Snake who is assigned to find the titular superweapon "Metal Gear", a bipedal walking tank with the ability to launch nuclear weapons.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-m-6">
              <img id="proPic" class="img-responsive img-thumbnail" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/08/Hideo_Kojima_20100702_Japan_Expo_1.jpg" alt="Hideo Kojima">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div  class="row thumb-border gutter-top">
